messages.message: Hey all -- does anyone know how I can figure out what the *oldest* deployed AI Hub version is? (_not_ IB Classic; only AI Hub)

for SaaS those versions are defined in the terraform-artifacts repo
https://github.com/instabase/terraform-artifacts/tree/main/automation/saas/stacks

For posterity, here are all the deployed versions:

```cs/mfichman❯ find . -print0 -type f -name '*.json' | xargs -n1 -0 jq '.release_version' | sort | uniq
